<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1876] pom file for scala 2.11 should reference a specific version</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1876</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the pom file specifies the following scala dependency for 2.11.&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.scala-lang&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;scala-library&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;2.11&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;compile&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
However, there is no 2.11 in maven central (there are only 2.11.1, 2.11.2, etc).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
